videoDetails.Title: The Tank That Ruled War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

War Thunder sometimes feels like a game dominated by a revolving door of overpowered vehicles, with one tank in particular making a very big impression. The Soviet ZSU-57-2 is a tank destroyer masquerading as an SPAA. 

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.
